<casebody firstpage="2184" lastpage="2184" xmlns="http://nrs.harvard.edu/urn-3:HLS.Libr.US_Case_Law.Schema.Case_Body:v1">
<parties id="p-1">
  In the Matter of Jeffrey Scott SCHWARTZ.
 </parties>
<docketnumber id="p-2">
  No. D-2951.
 </docketnumber>
<court id="p-3">
  Supreme Court of the United States
 </court>
<decisiondate id="p-4">
  May 22, 2017.
 </decisiondate>
<opinion id="p-5">
  Jeffrey Scott Schwartz, of San Diego, California, having requested to resign as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that his name be stricken from the roll of attorneys admitted to the practice of law before this Court. The Rule to Show Cause, is issued on February 21, 2017, is discharged.
 </opinion>

</casebody>
